  "title": "Who is the third",
  "sourceFile": "Waste_notes/whoisthethird_N.htm",
  "encoding": "windows-1252",
  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> </font><b>Who is\n        the third ...</b><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p>The following lines were stimulated by the account of\n        one of the Antarctic expeditions (I forget which, but I\n        think one of Shackleton's): it was related that the party\n        of explorers, at the extremity of their strength, had the\n        constant delusion that there was <i>one more member</i>\n        than could actually be counted. [Eliot's note] </p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td> </td>\n<td><a href=\"title_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Waste_A.htm\"><font>back to \"The Waste Land\" </font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
  "text": "Who is the third ... The following lines were stimulated by the account of one of the Antarctic expeditions (I forget which, but I think one of Shackleton's): it was related that the party of explorers, at the extremity of their strength, had the constant delusion that there was one more member than could actually be counted. [Eliot's note] back to \"The Waste Land\"",
